Here is a list of some of the most important and frequently used shortcuts for IntelliJ IDEA:

### Basic Navigation
- **Double Shift**: Search Everywhere
- **Ctrl + N** (Cmd + O on macOS): Find Class
- **Ctrl + Shift + N** (Cmd + Shift + O on macOS): Find File
- **Ctrl + Shift + Alt + N** (Cmd + Shift + Alt + O on macOS): Find Symbol
- **Alt + Right/Left Arrow** (Ctrl + Right/Left Arrow on macOS): Navigate to Next/Previous Editor Tab

### Code Editing
- **Ctrl + Space** (Cmd + Space on macOS): Basic Code Completion
- **Ctrl + Shift + Space** (Cmd + Shift + Space on macOS): Smart Code Completion
- **Ctrl + /** (Cmd + / on macOS): Comment/Uncomment Line
- **Ctrl + Shift + /** (Cmd + Shift + / on macOS): Comment/Uncomment Block
- **Ctrl + Y** (Cmd + Delete on macOS): Delete Line
- **Ctrl + D** (Cmd + D on macOS): Duplicate Line or Block
- **Ctrl + Shift + Up/Down** (Cmd + Shift + Up/Down on macOS): Move Line Up/Down
- **Ctrl + Alt + L** (Cmd + Option + L on macOS): Reformat Code
- **Ctrl + Shift + J** (Cmd + Shift + J on macOS): Join Lines

### Refactoring
- **Ctrl + Alt + Shift + T** (Cmd + Shift + T on macOS): Refactor This
- **Shift + F6** (Cmd + F6 on macOS): Rename
- **Ctrl + Alt + V** (Cmd + Option + V on macOS): Extract Variable
- **Ctrl + Alt + M** (Cmd + Option + M on macOS): Extract Method

### Running and Debugging
- **Shift + F10** (Ctrl + R on macOS): Run
- **Shift + F9** (Cmd + D on macOS): Debug
- **F8** (Cmd + Option + Right Arrow on macOS): Step Over
- **F7** (Cmd + Option + Down Arrow on macOS): Step Into
- **Shift + F8** (Cmd + Shift + Option + Right Arrow on macOS): Step Out
- **Alt + F9** (Cmd + Option + F9 on macOS): Run to Cursor

### Project and Code Structure
- **Alt + 1** (Cmd + 1 on macOS): Open Project Tool Window
- **Ctrl + Shift + F12** (Cmd + Shift + F12 on macOS): Toggle Tool Window
- **Ctrl + F12** (Cmd + F12 on macOS): File Structure
- **Ctrl + H** (Cmd + H on macOS): Type Hierarchy
- **Ctrl + Shift + H** (Cmd + Shift + H on macOS): Method Hierarchy
- **Ctrl + Alt + H** (Cmd + Option + H on macOS): Call Hierarchy

### General
- **Ctrl + Shift + A** (Cmd + Shift + A on macOS): Find Action
- **Alt + Enter** (Option + Enter on macOS): Show Intention Actions and Quick-Fixes
- **F2/Shift + F2** (F2/Shift + F2 on macOS): Next/Previous Highlighted Error
- **Ctrl + Tab** (Ctrl + Tab on macOS): Switch Between Tabs and Tool Windows

These shortcuts can significantly improve productivity by making it easier to navigate, edit, and refactor code quickly and efficiently.





Here's the table with dashed borders:

```
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| **Category**          | **Action**                         | **Windows/Linux**      | **macOS**              |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| **Basic Navigation**  | Search Everywhere                 | Double Shift           | Double Shift           |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                       | Find Class                        | Ctrl + N               | Cmd + O                |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                       | Find File                         | Ctrl + Shift + N       | Cmd + Shift + O        |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                       | Find Symbol                       | Ctrl + Shift + Alt + N | Cmd + Shift + Alt + O  |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                       | Navigate to Next/Previous Tab     | Alt + Right/Left Arrow | Ctrl + Right/Left Arrow|
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| **Code Editing**      | Basic Code Completion             | Ctrl + Space           | Cmd + Space            |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                       | Smart Code Completion             | Ctrl + Shift + Space   | Cmd + Shift + Space    |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                       | Comment/Uncomment Line            | Ctrl + /               | Cmd + /                |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                       | Comment/Uncomment Block           | Ctrl + Shift + /       | Cmd + Shift + /        |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                       | Delete Line                       | Ctrl + Y               | Cmd + Y                |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                       | Duplicate Line                    | Ctrl + D               | Cmd + D                |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                       | Move Line Up/Down                 | Shift + Alt + Up/Down  | Shift + Cmd + Up/Down  |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| **Refactoring**       | Rename                            | Shift + F6             | Shift + F6             |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
```